      • authenticateUsing

        @Beta
void authenticateUsing(Credentials credentials)
        Authenticate an HTTP Basic Auth dialog. Usage: driver.switchTo().alert().authenticateUsing(new UsernamePasswordCredentials("cheese", "secretGouda"));
        参数:
        credentials - - the credentials that will be passed to the Authentication prompt
